{code}
MongoDB::GridFSError: Error inserting file document: MongoDB::DuplicateKeyError: E11000 duplicate key error collection: foo.fs.files index: filename_1_uploadDate_1 dup key: { : "foo.txt", : new Date(1501713196000) }     (in cleanup) MongoDB::GridFSError: Error inserting file document: MongoDB::DuplicateKeyError: E11000 duplicate key error collection: foo.fs.files index: filename_1_uploadDate_1 dup key: { : "foo.txt", :  } at (eval 605) line 31, <DATA> line 1.
